{"type":"text","timestamp":1778985213677,"sessionID":"ses_1cc381f39ffeamsZb0CkayuqBK","part":{"id":"prt_e33c80fd30015erOcOeWWdl55s","messageID":"msg_e33c7fb8a001Ba1NpuzSY8kLPl","sessionID":"ses_1cc381f39ffeamsZb0CkayuqBK","type":"text","text":"Issue history makes the requested scope clear: these terms already exist, and the remaining requested fix is to change the `created_by` value from `GOC:vw` to bare `vw` on the affected terms, without touching unrelated content. I’m checking the current stanzas and loading the ontology-specific skills needed to verify the edit pattern before patching and validating.","time":{"start":1778985209811,"end":1778985213674}}}
